Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 28-03-2025

Map-And-Chat ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our application.

Information We Collect

Personal Information: We collect your name, email address, and profile picture when you sign up via Google or Facebook.

Usage Data: We collect information on how you use our services, such as interactions and preferences.

Location Data: If you grant permission, we collect your location to enhance map-based features.

How We Use Your Information

 To provide and improve our services.

To personalize user experiences.

To communicate with you regarding updates and support.

Third-Party Services

We use third-party authentication services like Google and Facebook. These services may collect and process data as per their own policies.

Data Retention

We retain your data as long as your account remains active. If you wish to delete your data, follow the instructions in the Data Deletion Policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions, contact us at usamaijaz2119@gmail.com.

